Add maybe_needs_cc_toolchain parameter to go_context() for lazy C/C++
toolchain resolution. Rules that do not use CGO in their own actions can
pass maybe_needs_cc_toolchain=False to skip invoking cgo_context_data_impl,
reducing unnecessary analysis-time work.

Source: https://github.com/bazel-contrib/rules_go/pull/4593

